<demos>
<name>DiscreteWavelets</name>
<type>toolbox</type>
<icon>$toolbox/matlab/icons/matlabicon.gif</icon>
<description isCdata="no">
	<p>
	The DiscreteWavelets Toolbox allows users to experiment with discrete wavelet
	transformations and use them in applications such as data/image compression, image edge detection,
	and signal/image denoising.  The material in the DiscreteWavelets Toolbox and demos below serves as 
	a supplement the text <i>Discrete Wavelet Transformations - An Elementary Approach with Applications</i>,
	(John J Wiley &amp; Sons, 2008), by Patrick J. Van Fleet.
	</p>	
</description>
<website>
	<a href="http://www.stthomas.edu/wavelets">Discrete Wavelets Web Site</a>
</website>

